## =========================================================
## FastAPI / Multi-RAG test file
## ETAP 8: Multi-RAG + per-agent retrieval + debug metadata
## =========================================================

### HEALTHCHECK
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/healthcheck
Accept: application/json

###

### LIST ALL AGENTS
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/agents
Accept: application/json

###

### LIST ALL DOCUMENTS
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/documents/hogwart
Accept: application/json

###

## =========================================================
## HR AGENT
## =========================================================

### HR / known fact
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "question": "How many days of holiday does each worker have?",
  "selected_agent": "hr"
}

###

### HR / isolation check
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "question": "Who is Frodo?",
  "selected_agent": "hr"
}

